## May 2019 Ballot Comment: https://fhircast.hl7.org/#event-catalog link doesn't link to an event catalog.

Submitted by Mitra Rocca; Terrie Reed
Chapter/section:
Url: https://fhircast.hl7.org/#event-catalog
Type: A-T

Summary: https://fhircast.hl7.org/#event-catalog link doesn't link to an event catalog.

Comment: The link to the "Event Catalog" seems to be broken. Since the event catalog is very difficult to maintain, it would useful to provide a grammar for generating
